{"tid":1820781,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"中醫醫暗瘡究竟work 5 work?","createTime":"2020-01-11T17:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T20:31:57.000Z","uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4501a6916b1c70433b26343668b0151d0059ed3f","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"我生咗暗瘡3-4年，乜藥膏都睇茶過，好奇怪地，每次一茶新藥膏就好D，持續茶就冇效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過西醫，食過藥，但係我頂唔順咁大粒嘅藥，次次都哽到，所以兩星期就放棄左。<br />\n<br />\n宜家想睇中醫，但係我見有人話食中藥D暗瘡會越出越多，係咪真？究竟食中藥有冇用？有冇過來人經歷？有冇中醫推介？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0846be791e4248bb42fa62e1085f9e61de3a91e","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"自推5次 1/5"},{"pid":"b78272f07b1405fed176421c9c64da943dd82a06","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"58283621283a250971b08004a935edb543a9167c","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:24:11.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"ac32f32dda7aa3405d98e9e1b78c4ec1b54fc7fd","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"14896f41019d973afa896b18de0ca29ac1b3179d","tid":1820781,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"5/5"},{"pid":"ae3951bd0e0915de5ff80c06ec2c95cb997d8721","tid":1820781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"植皮會work啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8e070252f789add56547efb92899867f8c2e08","tid":1820781,"uid":314021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"我自己就未